ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with Templar Restaurants Inc. Operating as The Keg Manor ** NCC **
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant two options commencing on July 1, 2018; and the second option to be for a period of fives years commencing on February 1, 2019, to extend an existing lease with TEMPLAR RESTAURANTS INC, operating as THE KEG MANOR to occupy a property located at 529 Richmond Road, in Ottawa.
